  <style>
    .spirals-page { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 6rem 1.5rem 4rem; }
    .spirals-page__eyebrow {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--accent);
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }
    .spirals-page__h1 {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 2.75rem);
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1.1;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      color: var(--fg);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .spirals-page__lede {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
      line-height: 1.65;
      max-width: 540px;
    }
    .spirals-grid {
      display: grid;
      gap: 1rem;
    }
    .spirals-card {
      display: block;
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: border-color 0.15s, box-shadow 0.15s;
    }
    .spirals-card:hover {
      border-color: var(--accent);
      box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(201,123,93,0.12);
    }
    .spirals-card__title {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--fg);
      margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
      line-height: 1.3;
    }
    .spirals-card:hover .spirals-card__title { color: var(--accent); }
    .spirals-card__desc {
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.55;
    }
    .spirals-cta {
      margin-top: 3rem;
      padding: 2rem;
      background: #2A2522;
      border-radius: 12px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 1rem;
    }
    .spirals-cta__text {
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: #FAF6F0;
      max-width: 420px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .spirals-cta__btn {
      display: inline-block;
      background: var(--accent);
      color: #fff;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      padding: 0.65rem 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 7px;
      text-decoration: none;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }
    .spirals-cta__btn:hover { background: #b56a4c; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/nav') %>

  <div class="spirals-page">
    <div class="spirals-page__eyebrow">Spirals</div>
    <h1 class="spirals-page__h1">The questions you Google at 11 PM.</h1>
    <p class="spirals-page__lede">
      Honest, terse answers to the anxious-attachment texting questions nobody answers well. No fluff. No "have you tried journaling?"
    </p>

    <div class="spirals-grid">
      <a href="/should-i-double-text" class="spirals-card">
        <div class="spirals-card__title">Should I double text?</div>
        <div class="spirals-card__desc">When the second message is fine, when it's not, and what you're actually trying to accomplish.</div>
      </a>

      <a href="/what-to-text-when-he-hasnt-replied" class="spirals-card">
        <div class="spirals-card__title">What to text when he hasn't replied</div>
        <div class="spirals-card__desc">The honest answer, with a rough timeline and what not to send.</div>
      </a>

      <a href="/why-do-i-overtext-when-anxious" class="spirals-card">
        <div class="spirals-card__title">Why do I overtext when anxious?</div>
        <div class="spirals-card__desc">What's happening neurologically when you can't stop texting — and what actually interrupts it.</div>
      </a>

      <a href="/should-i-text-him-first" class="spirals-card">
        <div class="spirals-card__title">Should I text him first?</div>
        <div class="spirals-card__desc">The question behind the question, and how to tell whether you're in the right state to reach out.</div>
      </a>

      <a href="/11pm-text-anxious-attachment" class="spirals-card">
        <div class="spirals-card__title">Why do I text at night? The 11 PM spiral.</div>
        <div class="spirals-card__desc">Why anxious attachment + nighttime is the worst combination — and what to do with the next 20 minutes.</div>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="spirals-cta">
      <div class="spirals-cta__text">
        Paste the message you're about to send. Get a verdict before it goes out.
      </div>
      <a href="/filter" class="spirals-cta__btn">Open HoldOff free →</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
